{"tid":1145852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跳船]  港航遞核數師辭職通知 羅兵咸永道或已辭任","createTime":"2019-05-09T01:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T11:26:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":95,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb5bb49a2c7fe8637b6dac10a5c03e23b51d77b","tid":1145852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"港航遞核數師辭職通知 羅兵咸永道或已辭任<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5cd3427bbde0b33646b9b320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finet.hk%2Fnewscenter%2Fnews_content%2F5cd3427bbde0b33646b9b320&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3efdc483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5cd3427bbde0b33646b9b320</a><br />\n<br />\n據公司註冊署申報文件顯示，香港航空於5月3日遞交一份標題為「核數師辭職通知」文件，該文件仍處於「待辦」狀況，未能公開查閱文件內容。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，現任港航核數師的羅兵咸永道會計師或已辭任， 至截稿前，羅兵咸永道沒有回應，而香港航空發言人則表示，公司最近更換其核數服務商以有效管理成本及滿足不斷變更的業務需求。"},{"pid":"4207a575f2843b3fab12ff4fb695025808527927","tid":1145852,"uid":48083,"like":206,"dislike":1,"score":205,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"核數師跳船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41789cc089cb42d7c6a9cdfa34c9f7dd0ee69bc5","tid":1145852,"uid":12021,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f91659866f63708c4249a65237a8f5a343cb6658","tid":1145852,"uid":59794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"唔知會有幾多核數佬係呢到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5febe51f57332e285cab9bcc8f0bf7174261cb0","tid":1145852,"uid":174767,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"4207a575f2843b3fab12ff4fb695025808527927","tid":1145852,"uid":48083,"like":206,"dislike":1,"score":205,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"核數師跳船<img 